{"tid":243430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"楊婉儀開辦，「雙非優先」幼稚園執笠","createTime":"2017-05-14T15:44:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-08T01:12:57.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1232,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4a41fd7e98307d385d6213b97e7bcf7a5e31b73e","tid":243430,"uid":22675,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T15:44:17.000Z","msg":"May 14, 2017 admin  0 Comment<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/hkjam.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/sketch-1494754342670.png?resize=1024%2C576\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fhkjam.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2Fsketch-1494754342670.png%3Fresize%3D1024%252C576&h=ea5de5c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前港姐冠軍楊婉儀與丈夫及其他生意伙伴合資開辦，講明「關注雙非童長途跋涉跨境讀書」，標榜優先安排雙非兒童就讀的Golden Gate國際幼稚園暨幼兒園，原來新年後已結業，據指幼稚園涉及不少金錢糾紛。<br />\n<br />\n但幼稚園結業未有打擊楊婉儀辦學的雄心，她指將與美國太空總署（NASA）合作辦學，取名「STEAM」，似乎十分強調科學方面的傳授。"},{"pid":"0d8c461139b7d66878cbc85f0c99a68366aaddae","tid":243430,"uid":72859,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T15:47:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4e122f0f4043b27824ba1d06d784aaa6d348be1","tid":243430,"uid":9385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T15:48:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76d24e1c571fdc4d16a4eb3f8c37d71350406f55","tid":243430,"uid":2076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T15:48:46.000Z","msg":"我真係恭喜你啊"},{"pid":"247355901fa2eedf9a8448620118869bd633af1c","tid":243430,"uid":31237,"like"