未註冊營運，楊婉儀就解釋話：「教育局已經嚟過學校，我哋冇違規，係順利嘅！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56691424&amp;category_guid=7018882&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170514\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56691424%26category_guid%3D7018882%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170514&d=sOSR1epLEapJbLCvIyWeddU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=32ce98a6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56691424%26category_guid%3D7018882%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170514&h=a2526260\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56691424&amp;category_guid=7018882&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170514</a><br />\n連登仔睇埋啲垃圾農場<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59af6609212a0dcb6f60e6b3e73520f2afa466dc","tid":243430,"uid":23021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T23:56:59.000Z","msg":"Skt好人<br />\n等我地快d睇我狼"},{"pid":"a99f0c64c81eabb8221414d00720d44e13f52725","tid":243430,"uid":23021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T23:57:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Skt好人<br />\n等我地快d睇我狼</blockquote><br />\n錯po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f37950ba56de41b0cc7531bcd9e2e0f8e1ed7a99","tid":243430,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T23:57:29.000Z","msg":"講到自己咁偉大<br />\n咪又係為左賺錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f4ab032afe810c11260b221c172bdde57fe06d4","tid":243430,"uid":2612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T00:02:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets